commit_list.message: Move ORMapView to iOS8 and make it a framework

Fix crash when calling observeValueForKeyPath on
MKMapView.

Always return a copy of the annotations array,
because uses might call addAnnotation or
removeAnnotation while iterating on annotations
via fast enumeration.
Recluster only once per RunLoop run.

Support setting default cluster view class, so
ORMapView can be used as a drop-in replacement
for SuperPin.

Fix ORClusterAnnotationView

View did not redraw when annotation changed.
Make project work with iOS SDK 6 and XCode 4.6.

Do not cluster if clustering is disabled.

This handles a possible race condition where the
clustering algorithm is still working in the
background and clusteringEnabled was set to NO in
the meantime.

Implement a basic example project.
